Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.07,0:14:16.00,Cartello BASE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs20\c&H12467F&\pos(466.968,269.187)}Casa di
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.07,0:14:16.00,Cartello BASE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs20\c&H12467F&\pos(468.072,284.094)}Watauki
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,così non ho avuto altra scelta che girarmi.
